OL,3,CNewcastle underground: Inside the
OL,4,Ctunnel running below the city
OL,6,FJulie Harrison went underground to
OL,7,Ffind out more about the varied history
OL,8,Fof Newcastle's Victoria Tunnel for
OL,10,FUnder the streets of Newcastle lies a
OL,11,Flittle-known tunnel which has been
OL,12,Fthere for generations.
OL,14,FStretching from the River Tyne to the
OL,15,FTown Moor, Victoria Tunnel was built
OL,16,Fto transport coal from Leazes Main
OL,17,FColliery in Spital Tongues.
