OL,3,CNewcastle underground: Inside the
OL,4,Ctunnel running below the city
OL,6,F"There were lots of issues with that
OL,7,Fcoal coming out of the ground. They
OL,8,Fwere haemorrhaging money."
OL,10,FWith costs making the project
OL,11,Funeconomically viable, they decided to
OL,12,Fbuild the tunnel in an old glacial
OL,13,Friverbed to save money.
OL,15,FIt opened in 1842 and was used until
OL,16,F1860, when the colliery closed.
OL,18,FAbandoned and forgotten about, the
OL,19,Ftunnel was disused until the Second
OL,20,FWorld War, when it was used as an air
OL,21,Fraid shelter.
