OL,6,FSince 2008, members of the public have
OL,7,Fbeen able to take guided tours, which
OL,8,Fare run by the Ouseburn Trust.
OL,10,FMr Byrne said: "It was a massive
OL,11,Fengineering achievement in the
OL,12,FVictorian era and then its got this
OL,13,Flovely history. It's something to be
OL,14,Fcelebrated really - why leave it as an
OL,15,Fempty space?"
